<F P=106> ["Special dispatch": "Zhu Rongji Inspects Chongqing"] </F>
  [Text] Chongqing, 7 Feb (TA KUNG PAO)--Zhu Rongji, member 
of the Standing Committee of the Political Bureau of the CPC 
Central Committee and vice premier of the State Council, is 
inspecting work in Chongqing. 
