<H3> <TI>   Jiangxi Governor Urges Concentration on Reform </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK0802023394 Nanchang Jiangxi People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 1100 GMT 6 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0802023394 </F>
<F P=104>  Nanchang Jiangxi People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] This morning the provincial party committee office, 
government office, and the propaganda department of the 
provincial party committee jointly held a meeting in Nanchang 
for journalists to celebrate the Spring Festival. Provincial 
leaders Wu Guanzheng, Zhu Zhihong, Lu Xiuzhen, Shu Shengyou, 
Zhong Qihuang, Chen Guizun, and Wu Yongle, reporters of central 
press units stationed in Jiangxi, provincial and city 
journalists and publishers, as well as some retired comrades 
from the press and publishing front gathered together to usher 
in the Spring Festival. 
  The meeting was presided over by Zhong Qihuang. Wu Guanzhen 
and Lu Xiuzhen spoke at the meeting. 
  In his speech, Governor Wu Guanzhen fully confirmed the 
province's achievements in last year's press and publicity work. 
He thanked central press unit reporters stationed in Jiangxi 
and Jiangxi reporters for their hard work and expressed his 
Lunar New Year greetings to them. 
  He stressed: In this year's economic work, the province 
should pay attention to three main points: The first is 
strengthening agricultural and rural work to ensure an increase 
in peasant income. The second is strengthening basic facilities 
construction to improve Jiangxi's investment environment in 
three to five years. The third is concentrating efforts on 
reform, opening up, introducting foreign capital, and expanding 
exports. 
  He hoped that central press unit reporters stationed in 
Jiangxi as well as provincial and city reporters would make 
further efforts to give wide publicity to Jiangxi's development. 
  In his speech, Lu Xiuzhen requested Jiangxi reporters to 
continue to give publicity to Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of 
building socialism with Chinese characteristics, to uphold the 
policy of unity, stability, boosting the morale, and positive 
dissemination, to strengthen guidance over publicity, to 
properly organize reports on reform, to propagate Jiangxi's 
achievements overseas, and to improve the ranks of journalists. 

</TEXT>

