<F P=100> Central-South Region </F>
<H3> <TI>   Hunan Defense Science, Technology Industry Growing </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK0802035694 Changsha Hunan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0802035694 </F>
<F P=104>  Changsha Hunan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] In 1993, the province's total national defense 
science and technology industrial output value registered a 
growth 31.86 percent higher than the province's average 
industrial output value growth, while the total amount of taxes 
and profits realized by the province's national defense science 
and technology industry recorded a 267 percent increase over the 
year before. 
  Yang Zhengwu, provincial party committee deputy secretary, 
at 
a provincial national defense science and technology industry 
conference being held at the moment, delivered a speech in which 
he called on all national defense science and technology 
industrial enterprises to establish more lateral economic 
associations in various forms within the province; take the 
initiative to contract more projects of the province's "huge 
dragon" and "torch" programs; make persistent efforts to do away 
with rigid and conservative ideological concepts; cultivate a 
strong sense of market competition; adapt itself more to Hunan's 
overall economic growth, major trades and professions 
development, and international economic development as well; and 
make unremitting efforts to open up new vistas. [passage 
omitted] 

