<AU>   FBIS-CHI-94-026 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  8 Feb 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Economic &amp; Agricultural </F>
<H3> <TI>   Li Peng Signs State Council Decree No. 143 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0802092394 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0920 
GMT 2 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0802092394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>


