<F P=103> HK0702133894 </F>
<F P=104>  Xining Qinghai People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] In the provincial Scientific and Technological 
Activity Center on the afternoon of 5 February, the provincial 
science and technology association, the provincial labor 
department, and the provincial planning commission joinly held a 
tea party for people from scientific and technological circles 
in Xining. Provincial party and government leaders -- including 
Yin Kesheng, Yao Xiangcheng, Yang Maojia, La Bingli, and Bainma 
Dandzin -- attended. [passage omitted] 
  On behalf of the provincial science and technology 
association, the provincial labor department, and the provincial 
