contributions to economic construction and social development. 
Our economy needs to be developed, and our science and 
technology need to be invigorated. As Qinghai is economically 
and culturally backward, the role of science and technology is 
particularly important. To narrow the gap between 
technologically advanced regions and ourselves, we must, in many 
aspects, rely on advanced science and technology, develop and 
expand the ranks of scientific and technological personnel, and 
improve the quality of the entire laborers. In the new 
situation of establishing the socialist market economic 
structure, science and technology also face a test. [passage 
omitted] 

