<H3> <TI>   Deng Xiaoping Meets Officials During Stay in Shanghai </TI></H3>
<H4>   Greets Local Officials </H4>
<F P=102> OW0902111394 Beijing XINHUA in English 1045 GMT 9 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0902111394 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Shanghai, Feburary 9 (XINHUA) -- Deng Xiaoping 
appeared at a gathering here this afternoon, exchanging Spring 
Festival greetings with local officials and retirees. 
  This is the seventh successive year Deng spends the 
traditional Spring Festival in Shanghai. 
  Deng, who is now 89 and in good health, inspected Shanghai's 
Pudong New Area and ascended the newly built Yangpu Bridge on 
December 13 last year. 

</TEXT>

