Language: <F P=105>Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video; from the "National News </F>
Hookup" program] 
  [Text] Li Peng, member of the CPC Central Committee 
Political Bureau Standing Committee and premier, who has just 
returned to Beijing after an inspection tour in other parts of 
the country, came to the residences of Comrades Peng Zhen and 
Wan Li this morning to wish them happy New Year and Spring 
Festival. [video shows medium close-ups of Li Peng and Peng 
Zhen exchanging greetings. Peng Zhen is seen sitting in a 
wheelchair pushed by a young man. Video then shows Ding Guangen 
and Luo Gan shaking Peng Zhen's hand] 
  Premier Li Peng presented bouquets to Comrades Peng Zhen and 
Wan Li and wished them good health, a happy New Year, and 
success in everything. 
  He also briefed the two veteran comrades on the domestic 
situation and the series of general and specific policies which 
the party Central Committee and the State Council have adopted 
for economic development, reform, and opening up. Li Peng also 
attentively listened to their views and suggestions on various 
projects. [video shows close-ups of Peng Zhen and Li Peng 
