appears to be immobile. Video then cuts to show medium 
close-ups of Li Peng visiting Wan Li and close-ups of them 
having a conversation across a small table] 
  Comrades Peng Zhen and Wan Li expressed satisfaction about 
the work accomplished by the CPC Central Committee and the State 
Council. They were also pleased with China's reform, opening 
