opportunity to deepen reform, open up wider to the outside 
world, expedite development, and maintain stability -- which the 
CPC Central Committee has set for this year's projects. They 
hoped the party Central Committee and the State Council will, on 
the basis of the successes they have accomplished, continue to 
work hard and lead people of all nationalities in the country to 
work with one heart and one mind and achieved even greater 
success in building a strong country. 
  Ding Guangen, member of the CPC Central Committee Political 
Bureau and Secretariat; Luo Gan, state councillor, and 
responsible comrades of relevant departments also visited 
Comrades Peng Zhen and Wan Li. 

