<H3> <TI>   Provinces Hold Forums on Double-Support Work </TI></H3>
<H4>   Hunan Holds Forum </H4>
<F P=102> HK0702150594 Changsha Hunan People's Radio Network in 
Mandarin 2300 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> HK0702150594 </F>
<F P=104>  Changsha Hunan People's Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Mandarin </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Yesterday morning [3 February], the provincial 
party committee and government held a forum for provincial 
party, government, and military leaders, leaders of the armed 
forces units stationed in Hunan, leaders of the Changsha City 
CPC Committee, and comrades in charge of the relevant provincial 
departments. They gathered to discuss the close relations 
between soldiers and civilians, as well as double-support work. 
  Provincial party Secretary Wang Maolin chaired and addressed 
the forum. He said: Hunan was an important place of origin for 
the founding of the Chinese armed forces and was the native 
place of our great leader, Chairman Mao. It has always had the 
fine tradition of supporting the Army and giving preferential 
treatment to the families of soldiers and martyrs, and of 
supporting the government and cherishing the people. Both in 
the revolutionary war years and in the period of peaceful 
construction, the Hunan people have united with the People's 
Army, shared weal and woe with it, and established deep feelings 
with it. In recent years, officers and soldiers stationed in 
Hunan have developed the fine tradition of supporting the 
government and cherishing the people, have taken an active part 
in the province's spiritual and material civilizations, and have 
made major contributions to maintaining social order, providing 
relief aid to disaster-stricken areas, helping the poor, 
carrying out key construction projects, and invigorating Hunan. 
Wang Maolin stressed these three points: First, double-support 
work should be taken as a major matter that has an important 
bearing on the overall situation and should be done well. 
Second, focusing on economic construction, we should carry out 
double-support work and the activity of building civilized units 
and villages. Third, it is necessary to serve the construction 
of the armed forces wholeheartedly. 
  Provincial party deputy secretary and Governor Chen Bangzhu 
also spoke at the forum. 

</TEXT>

